query:
/*+  */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('drupal',
'english',
'mathoverflow',
'serverfault')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('apache-2.2',
'commerce',
'domain-name-system',
'forms',
'grammar',
'networking',
'nginx',
'taxonomy-terms',
'windows')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Announcer',
'Autobiographer',
'Famous Question',
'Good Answer',
'Good Question',
'Popular Question',
'Revival')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
